/>&nbsp; &nbsp;+ ldy #0<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; ; oamIndex is a variable tracking how far you've written<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; ; into shadow OAM (customarily at $0200-$02FF)<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; ldx oamIndex<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;@loop:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; ; If you have the address of an array in a zero page pointer,<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; ; you use the (d),y addressing mode and increase Y to go<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; ; to the next byte.<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; lda (t0+0), y&nbsp; ;&lt;-- INDIRECT INDEXED ADDRESSING<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; iny<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; ;ect. start<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; clc<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; adc oY<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; sta sprite, x&nbsp; ;&lt;-- ABSOLUTE INDEXED ADDRESSING<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; inx<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; lda (t0+0), y<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; iny<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; sta sprite, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; inx<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; lda (t0+0), y<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; iny<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; sta sprite, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; inx<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; lda (t0+0), y<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; iny<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; clc<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; adc onscreenX+0<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; sta sprite, x<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; inx<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; ;end ect.&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; dec t2<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; bne @loop<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; stx oamIndex<br />+end: rts ;end of draw_sprite<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <br />&nbsp; ;/*************************<br />&nbsp; ;&nbsp; &nbsp;hide sprite 0<br />&nbsp; ;*************************/<br />&nbsp; hide_sprite:<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; lda #240<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; sta sprite+0<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; rts ;end of hide_sprite<br />&nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp; <br />&nbsp; ;/*************************<br />&nbsp; ;&nbsp; &nbsp;show sprite 0<br />&nbsp; ;*************************/